{"tid":2397344,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華傳收1億人仔玩抖音 為新戲宣傳犯規被罰","createTime":"2021-02-06T10:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T12:49:11.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5241b6b4f62806942bc1830a452ee324d530cb39","tid":2397344,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"天王劉德華上月開抖音，由於這是他出道以來首個全球個人社交賬號，所以兩天迅吸逾4,000萬fans關注，風頭一時無兩。有傳劉德華以過億人仔開抖音，收得天價當然要賣力，出名勤力的他，早前一連上載3條短片，反應超理想，甚至一度榮登抖音熱門明星賬號第1名。不過，劉德華在上載第5條短片時，就因為在片中落了水印及有廣告連結，為新戲《人潮洶湧》宣傳，結果觸犯平台規則，因此被降權， 抖音官方限制其短片流量，令該片能觸及的人數大跌，相比起他之前公開的4條短片、平均每條逾2,000萬的流量來計，第5條片只得4分1約500多萬，數字相差甚遠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210206/BDNOXBPPNVF63AURCXIB6QRCIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210206%2FBDNOXBPPNVF63AURCXIB6QRCIA%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMITUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=02f49af5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210206%2FBDNOXBPPNVF63AURCXIB6QRCIA%2F&h=504f0c8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210206/BDNOXBPPNVF63AURCXIB6QRCIA/</a>"},{"pid":"b36762397a0490ae16fd3a85698221357e20537e","tid":2397344,"uid":137694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMC9KLQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMC9KLQ.png&h=095643d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅志祥真係完美演繹咩叫廋死嘅駱駝比馬大"}]}